== scraps

Scraps is a project intended for personal reuse of code that we use day to day
basis. Here the written code has many intentions. The code written here can be
used in any ruby project. The whole idea is to create a high standard codebase
which improves your efficiency in coding. You can just refer the code or reuse
the code.

The code should be able to meet the latest ruby language standards.
The code should be documented properly.
The code should solve the problems in a general way.

